 reminds us in this inspiring book why those values are worth fighting for.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Mrz 2023) 0aLiberalismy21st century. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / Political Ideologies / Conservatism & Liberalism.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2023z978311074978640uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/9780300269116?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300269116423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300269116/original  a978-3-11-074978-6  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2023b2023  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY